{"tid":1229611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"環球時報：華盛頓為香港設置新陷阱 其心可誅","createTime":"2019-06-16T03:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T04:07:48.000Z","uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"237a8c32b4ec6cc52236fdc2bd298f41b112e9b4","tid":1229611,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:45:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/6/1560574514_E1-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F6%2F1560574514_E1-1280w.jpg&h=b5792b92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府提出修訂《逃犯條例》草案，引起社會極大爭議，觸發市民大規模遊行，以及12日的嚴重衝突。美國跨黨派國會議員周四(13日)提出《香港人權與民主法案》(The Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act)。《環球時報》今日發表以「華盛頓為香港設置新陷阱，其心可誅」為題發表評論指，法案的核心內容是要求美國政府每年審視香港的自治狀態，主要是檢視香港的人權和民主標準，從而決定是否維持香港所享有的特殊待遇，這待遇是指美國把香港作為一個獨立關稅區來對待。<br />\n<br />\n文章批評美國國會的做法非常陰毒，是要把香港變成對中國大陸施壓的新槓桿，同時試圖挑撥香港民眾對內地社會的怨氣，制造北京威脅到香港獨立關稅區地位的虛假印象。想給當前的香港局勢火上加油。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E7%92%B0%E7%90%83%E6%99%82%E5%A0%B1%EF%BC%9A%E8%8F%AF%E7%9B%9B%E9%A0%93%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%A8%AD%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%B0%E9%99%B7%E9%98%B1-%E5%85%B6%E5%BF%83%E5%8F%AF%E8%AA%85-176500\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E7%2592%25B0%25E7%2590%2583%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A0%25B1%25EF%25BC%259A%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%259B%259B%25E9%25A0%2593%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%2599%25B7%25E9%2598%25B1-%25E5%2585%25B6%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%25AA%2585-176500&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2Fhtey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=4dc3a6fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E7%92%B0%E7%90%83%E6%99%82%E5%A0%B1%EF%BC%9A%E8%8F%AF%E7%9B%9B%E9%A0%93%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%A8%AD%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%B0%E9%99%B7%E9%98%B1-%E5%85%B6%E5%BF%83%E5%8F%AF%E8%AA%85-176500</a>"},{"pid":"d0312d7262c5b9d7e5